items.title: Awesome Computational Biology
items.content_text:
### Drug Response Prediction / Compound Protein Interaction

*   [TransformerCPI (⭐144)](https://github.com/lifanchen-simm/transformerCPI) - A library for Compound Protein Interaction prediction using Transformer.

### Drug Response Prediction / Pre-trained embedding

*   [Evolutionary Scale Modeling (⭐3.7k)](https://github.com/facebookresearch/esm) - a library for protein embeddings.
*   [ChemBERTa-2 (⭐458)](https://github.com/seyonechithrananda/bert-loves-chemistry) - a library for chemical embeddingg and prediction.

### Drug Response Prediction / LLM for biology

*   [AI4Chem/ChemLLM-7B-Chat](https://huggingface.co/AI4Chem/ChemLLM-7B-Chat) - LLM for chemical and molecule science
*   [BioGPT (⭐4.4k)](https://github.com/microsoft/BioGPT) - LLM for Biomedical text generation

items.title: Awesome Cyber Security University
items.content_text:
### Free Beginner Red Team Path / Level 2 - Tooling

*   [Web Scanning](https://tryhackme.com/room/rustscan) - Learn the basics of automated web scanning.
*   [Metasploit](https://tryhackme.com/room/metasploitintro) - An introduction to the main components of the Metasploit Framework.

### Free Beginner Blue Team Path / Level 3 - Beginner Forensics, Threat Intel & Cryptography

*   [Threat Intelligence 101](https://tryhackme.com/room/cyberthreatintel) - Introduction to Cyber Threat Intelligence.
*   [Threat Intelligence Tools](https://tryhackme.com/room/threatinteltools) - Explore different OSINT tools used to conduct security threat assessments and investigations.

items.title: Awesome Zsh Plugins
items.content_text:
### Plugins / [superconsole](https://github.com/alexchmykhalo/superconsole) - Windows-only

*   [terminal-app (⭐12)](https://github.com/the8/terminal-app.zsh) - A plugin for integrating with the new macOS El Capitan Terminal.app features.

### Themes / [superconsole](https://github.com/alexchmykhalo/superconsole) - Windows-only

*   [bigshrimp (⭐2)](https://github.com/taksyon/BigShrimp-zsh-theme) - A clear and concise theme that includes decorators for username\@host, current directory and `git` status.
*   [gaia (⭐5)](https://github.com/gcaracuel/gaia.zsh-theme) - Originally a fork of [Bureau (⭐40)](https://github.com/isqua/bureau) adds new virtual environments info to the prompt: Kubernetes, virtualenv, rbenv and Java versions. Includes `git` status integration.
*   [glider (⭐1)](https://github.com/MrRedacted/zsh-glider) - Based on [strug (⭐2)](https://github.com/triplepointfive/oh-my-zsh/blob/master/themes/strug.zsh-theme). Includes decorators for `git` status, username, hostname and current directory.
items.content_html:
Plugins / superconsole - Windows-only

  • terminal-app (⭐12) - A plugin for integrating with the new macOS El Capitan Terminal.app features.

Themes / superconsole - Windows-only

  • bigshrimp (⭐2) - A clear and concise theme that includes decorators for username@host, current directory and git status.
  • gaia (⭐5) - Originally a fork of Bureau (⭐40) adds new virtual environments info to the prompt: Kubernetes, virtualenv, rbenv and Java versions. Includes git status integration.
  • glider (⭐1) - Based on strug (⭐2). Includes decorators for git status, username, hostname and current directory.
